2007-07-30 06:28  aleidinger

	* Makefile.in, aclocal.m4, ACM/Makefile.in, ACM/ADbg/Makefile.in,
	  ACM/ddk/Makefile.in, ACM/tinyxml/Makefile.in, Dll/Makefile.in,
